I was using "org.eclipse.jface.databinding I20060131-0800" from CVS repository for next UserCase. I needed 2 comboboxes Country and Area, and after selection of Country, Area combo must change it`s content to the list of Areas of selected Country.

I`ve used next code:

class Country {
   private String Name;
   private Area[] areaCodes;
   ... get/set...
}

class Area {
   private String name;
   ... get/set ...
}

class Catalog {
   private Country[] countries;
   ... get/set ...
}


// bind List of countries (from catalog)
dbc.bind(cViewer,  new Property(catalog, "countries"),  null);

// create updatable for the current selection
IUpdatable currentSelection = dbc.createUpdatable(
     new Property(cViewer, ViewersProperties.SINGLE_SELECTION));


// bind Area combo list of Areas to the area codes of the current selection
dbc.bind(aViewer,
     new Property(currentSelection, "areaCodes", Area.class, Boolean.TRUE),
     null);

